data.description: This is a single-family manufactured home with a great location, a large fenced backyard, and many updates including a new roof that was installed on 10-19-23. The home is located in a quiet area, where the area behind the home is a nature preserve, which means that you will never have homes behind your house. The home has a fresh paint throughout, a new water heater, new laminate flooring and new carpet throughout, new kitchen cabinets and new kitchen appliances.
